overview: The story of how humans are immigrants from another place, a  planet  square  as  a  box  from  which  we  had  to  evacuate.  We  no  longer  remember  the  square  planet,  but  keep  building  square boxes here on Earth. Nora is a rebellious teen-aged girl struggling to find a sense of identity, she is searching for some-one that will understand.
title: Origin of Man
